//SettingHowToUseActivity Find parking location
1. Use the search menu. 2. A list of malls that provide parking will appear. In addition, you can search for parking spaces based on nearby locations by clicking the blue button next to the search menu. 3. Select a parking location.
Make a Payment
1. Use the barcode obtained after filling in the booking data then scan it. 2. Select the payment method you want. 3. Click pay now.
